<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uk">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VM1 — Командний сервер</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            background: #0d1117;
            color: #c9d1d9;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 90%;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .header {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #21262d;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #58a6ff;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #8b949e;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background: #161b22;
            border: 1px solid #21262d;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card-title {
            color: #8b949e;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .card-value {
            color: #e6edf3;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .services {
            background: #161b22;
            border: 1px solid #21262d;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .service-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #21262d;
        }

        .service-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .status-dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background: #3fb950;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 12px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .service-name {
            color: #e6edf3;
            font-size: 14px;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .service-port {
            color: #8b949e;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #8b949e;
            font-size: 12px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #21262d;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #1f6feb;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 11px;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-left: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="title">VM1 — Командний сервер <span class="badge">active</span></div>
            <div class="subtitle">Метод автоматизованого розгортання IT-інфраструктури з використанням технологій IaC</div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">Hostname</div>
                <div class="card-value">{{ ansible_hostname }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">IP Address</div>
                <div class="card-value">{{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">Operating System</div>
                <div class="card-value">{{ ansible_distribution }} {{ ansible_distribution_version }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-title">Hardware</div>
                <div class="card-value">{{ ansible_processor_vcpus }} CPU | {{ (ansible_memtotal_mb / 1024) | round(1) }} GB RAM</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="services">
            <div class="card-title" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">Активні сервіси</div>
            <div class="service-item">
                <div class="status-dot"></div>
                <div class="service-name">Nginx</div>
                <div class="service-port">порт 8888</div>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
                <div class="status-dot"></div>
                <div class="service-name">Fail2ban</div>
                <div class="service-port">захист SSH</div>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
                <div class="status-dot"></div>
                <div class="service-name">Node Exporter</div>
                <div class="service-port">порт 9101</div>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
                <div class="status-dot"></div>
                <div class="service-name">rsyslog</div>
                <div class="service-port">логування</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            Курсант 223 навчальної групи солдат  Місяць Анна | Дипломна робота 2026
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
